      <title>摩根大通资产管理公司预计股市将在 2025 年持续走高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/jpmorgan-asset-management-sees-stock-market-rolling-through-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[投资者可以预期，即使经过激烈的上涨，标准普尔 500 指数自 2023 年初以来已上涨超过 50%，明年美国股市仍将继续上涨，因为涨幅将超越受欢迎的大型科技领头羊。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/jpmorgan-asset-management-sees-stock-market-rolling-through-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:32:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
