      <title>Dart 称央行购买推动金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/central-bank-buying-drives-up-gold-prices-dart-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛全球大宗商品研究联席主管萨曼莎·达特 (Samantha Dart) 表示，央行购买黄金正在推高黄金价格。她预计到 2025 年底，黄金价格将达到每盎司 3,000 美元。她正在接受“彭博监测”采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-21/central-bank-buying-drives-up-gold-prices-dart-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:20:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
