      <title>大众汽车工会呼吁 12 月罢工以应对裁员争议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vw-warning-strikes-to-start-in-december-as-talks-continue</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于工会领袖和管理层未能就如何削减该汽车制造商同名品牌的成本达成协议，德国各地大众汽车工人计划从下月初开始举行大规模罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-21/vw-warning-strikes-to-start-in-december-as-talks-continue</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Nov 2024 16:15:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司陷入困境，英伟达股价涨势暂停：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司 (Nvidia Corp.) 的强劲涨势因前景不及华尔街的高预期而遭遇挫折，大型科技股因此感到不安。乌克兰战争也让投资者感到不安，引发了石油和黄金的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 22:42:35 GMT</pubDate>
